Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Bush to be Reagan's running mate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w48g
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jul 1980
Ford loses out to Bush as running mate for Reagan in race for the White House. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.